Sonic Adventure 2;Sonic Adventure 2;Sonic Adventure 2;;;OK;images\Sonic Adventure 2 (2012).webp;;Steam;Sonic Team USA;Sega;19/11/2012;Sonic Adventure 2 is the sequel to Sonic Adventure. It was the final Sonic game for the Dreamcast after Sega discontinued the console. Two new playable characters were introduced, Shadow and Rouge, who would go on to become two of the most recurring characters in the Sonic series. The story features good vs evil: Sonic, Tails and Knuckles attempt to save the world, while Shadow, Doctor Eggman and Rouge attempt to conquer it. The levels are divided into three gameplay styles: fast-paced platforming for Sonic and Shadow, multi-directional shooting for Tails and Eggman, and action-exploration for Knuckles and Rouge.;Adventure, Platform;no_section;steam_213610
Galactic Civilizations I Ultimate Edition;Galactic Civilizations I: Ultimate Edition;Galactic Civilizations I Ultimate Edition;;videos\Galactic Civilizations I Ultimate Edition (2012).mp4;OK;images\Galactic Civilizations I Ultimate Edition (2012).webp;;Steam;Stardock Entertainment;Stardock Entertainment;14/08/2012;Galactic Civilizations is a space based strategy game in which you are in control of humanity's destiny.;Strategy;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/214150/8631/11bb0f31f18c9abb2b4e3f4baa39d8616433a572/1751259703/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447356416;steam_214150
Little Nightmares Enhanced Edition;Little Nightmares Enhanced Edition;Little Nightmares Enhanced Edition;;;OK;images\Little Nightmares Enhanced Edition (2025).webp;;Steam;Tarsier Studios;Bandai Namco Entertainment;24/06/2025;"Little Nightmares is a puzzle-platform horror adventure game developed by Tarsier Studios and published by Bandai Namco Entertainment. Set in a mysterious world, Little Nightmares follows the journey of Six, a hungry little girl who must escape the Maw, an iron vessel inhabited by monstrous, twisted beings.

The Enhanced Edition improves upon the original release by supporting 4K resolution at 60 FPS and enhancing visual effects, including RTX reflections, improved water effects, additional particles, and volumetric lighting.

It also offers players the option to choose between Quality Mode or Performance Mode, allowing them to prioritize either visual fidelity or frame rate based on their preferences.";Adventure, Platform, Puzzle;no_section;steam_2149010
