Project CARS;Project CARS 2;Project CARS;;videos\Project CARS (2015).mp4;OK;images\Project CARS (2015).webp;;Steam;Slightly Mad Studios;Bandai Namco Entertainment;22/09/2017;Project CARS 2 is the next evolution in the award-winning racing series, featuring the most iconic cars under the most thrilling of conditions to deliver the “Ultimate Driver Journey” experience. Created by gamers, tested by world-class racing drivers, and the definitive choice of e-Sports pros – Project CARS 2 brings together the essence of motorsports racing in the most beautiful, authentically crafted, and technically advanced racing game on the planet.;Simulator, Racing;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/234630/35353/f77c14887ed2edb2a8f359cffdc83ec4bf9bd008/1751259408/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447374004;steam_234630, steam_378860
