Framed Collection;Framed Collection;Framed Collection;;videos\Framed Collection (2018).mp4;OK;images\Framed Collection (2018).webp;;Steam;Loveshack Entertainment;Surprise Attack Games;17/05/2018;"""The Framed Collection is the compilation of the the critically acclaimed, multi-award winning, noir-puzzle games Framed and Framed 2, where you re-arrange panels of a comic book to change the outcome of the story.

