RWBY Grimm Eclipse;RWBY: Grimm Eclipse;RWBY Grimm Eclipse;;videos\RWBY Grimm Eclipse (2016).mp4;OK;images\RWBY Grimm Eclipse (2016).webp;;Steam;Rooster Teeth Games;Rooster Teeth Games;05/07/2016;"RWBY: Grimm Eclipse is a 4 player Co-op, hack-n-slash game based upon Rooster Teeth’s international hit series RWBY.

Get ready for intense combat action as you battle Grimm across familiar locations of Remnant including new areas never before seen in the show. Play as Ruby, Weiss, Blake, and Yang in this character-driven adventure that explores new storylines, new Grimm types, and a new villain!

The gameplay takes inspiration from games such as Dynasty Warriors and Left 4 Dead offering over-the-top combat along with engaging missions and storytelling.";Adventure, Indie, Hack and slash/Beat 'em up, Fighting;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/418340/63875/b9d607d8365d13069c0a79e5fd237e1a57a1bf2c/1750527946/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1467393584;steam_418340
Pankapu;Pankapu;Pankapu;;videos\Pankapu (2016).mp4;OK;images\Pankapu (2016).webp;;Steam;Too Kind Studio;Plug In Digital;21/09/2016;"Pankapu is a 2D platform/action game, narrative and episodic:

In a world full of Dreams and Nightmares, a tiny warrior has to fight for the safety of his homeland. However, the real purpose of his his quest, beyond the struggle of good and evil, is the mental health of a traumatized child.

Told in the manner of a fable read to a child, the game has two levels of reading: the story of Pankapu, epic and naive, and the second one, about Djaha’rell life, the one to whom the tale is told, dark and tragic.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Indie, Platform;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/418670/73513/480996ab9b477997bde1371849ba8abb8431d98a/1751280912/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1505983483;steam_418670
