Marvel's Guardians of the Galaxy The Telltale Series;Marvel's Guardians of the Galaxy: The Telltale Series;Marvel's Guardians of the Galaxy The Telltale Series;;videos\Marvels Guardians of the Galaxy The Telltale Series (2017).mp4;OK;images\Marvels Guardians of the Galaxy The Telltale Series (2017).webp;;Steam;Telltale Games;Telltale Games;18/04/2017;"Marvel's Guardians of the Galaxy: The Telltale Series is a brand new story of the universe's unlikeliest heroes: Star-Lord, Gamora, Drax, Rocket, and Groot. In the wake of an epic battle, the Guardians discover an artifact of unspeakable power. Each of them has a reason to desire this relic, as does a ruthless enemy who is the last of her kind, and who will stop at nothing to tear it from their hands.

