“Syberia: The World Before is something to be excited for if you are a returning fan to the series or someone who is looking for something to fill that classic adventure-game-sized hole in your heart.""<br>
– <a href=""https://www.ign.com/articles/syberia-the-world-before-the-final-preview-pc""><b>IGN US</b></a><br>
