Deliver Us Mars (Epic Games Store);Deliver Us Mars;Deliver Us Mars;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\DELIVER US\Deliver Us Mars (Epic Games Store);;OK;images\Deliver Us Mars (2023).webp;;Epic Games Store;KeokeN Interactive;Frontier Foundry;02/02/2023;Deliver Us Mars is a sci-fi adventure game developed by KeokeN Interactive and released in 2023. It is a sequel to Deliver Us the Moon and follows the story of astronaut Kathy Johanson as she embarks on a mission to Mars to recover powerful colony ships known as the ARKs, which were stolen by a group called the Outward. The game combines exploration, puzzle-solving, and platforming elements as players navigate the harsh Martian environment and uncover the mysteries surrounding the disappearance of the ARKs.;Adventure, Indie, Platform;;epic_9d943a160fa841859ac5c1f233789fcb
