1994 - System Shock, Classic (Steam);System Shock: Classic;System Shock Classic;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SYSTEM SHOCK\1994 - System Shock, Classic (Steam);;OK;images\System Shock Classic (1994).webp;1994;Steam;Looking Glass Studios;Electronic Arts, Origin Systems, Dong Seo Interactive;22/09/1994;A seminal cyberpunk first-person exploratory adventure game with RPG elements in which, waking up in the Citadel Space Station, a lone hacker has to survive corrupted enemies and collect audio logs and equipment from former station workers in order to shut down SHODAN, the station's artificial intelligence that has killed everyone on board and now intends to destroy the world.;Role-playing (RPG), Shooter;;steam_410700
1999 - System Shock 2 (Steam);System Shock 2;System Shock 2;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SYSTEM SHOCK\1999 - System Shock 2 (Steam);videos\System Shock 2 (1999).mp4;OK;images\System Shock 2 (1999).webp;1999;Steam;Irrational Games, Looking Glass Studios;Electronic Arts, Nightdive Studios;11/08/1999;"System Shock 2 is a first-person shooter action role-playing survival horror video game for Microsoft Windows, Apple OS X and Linux. The title was designed by Ken Levine and co-developed by Irrational Games and Looking Glass Studios. Originally intended to be a standalone title, its story was changed during production into a sequel to the 1994 PC game System Shock; the alterations were made when Electronic Arts—who owned the System Shock franchise rights—signed on as publisher. System Shock 2 was released on August 11, 1999, in North America.";Role-playing (RPG), Shooter;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/238210/11489/5163a1ac1c44a160e91d8911fbd60c020d604ac0/1751246660/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1447357878;steam_238210
2015 - System Shock, Enhanced Edition (Steam);System Shock: Enhanced Edition;System Shock Enhanced Edition;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\SYSTEM SHOCK\2015 - System Shock, Enhanced Edition (Steam);videos\System Shock Enhanced Edition (2015).mp4;OK;images\System Shock Enhanced Edition (2015).webp;2015;Steam;Looking Glass Studios;Nightdive Studios, Limited Run Games;22/09/2015;"Exactly twenty one years after its first release, System Shock is back! The Enhanced Edition adds a modern touch to this true classic gem, without taking anything from its unmistakable atmosphere. See for yourself that the game that has been called the benchmark for intelligent first-person gaming, has lost nothing of its ability to keep you on the edge of your seat.

You're a renowned hacker, the most notorious cyberspace thief in the corporate world. Caught during a risky break-in, you become indentured to Diego, a greedy Trioptium exec who bankrolls a rare cyberjack implant operation. After six months in a healing coma, you awaken to the twisted aftermath of a terrible disaster. Where are the surgeons? Why is the station in such disrepair? Slowly, the chilling realization that something is very wrong creeps over you.

Once a prime corporate research facility, Citadel now teems with mindless cyborgs, robots and terribly mutated beings, all programmed to serve SHODAN, a ruthless A.I. There's scarcely time to think before it unleashes the first terror...";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure, Puzzle, Shooter;https://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/410710/182864/d0c2973a445aa651b32b363791ec7eba7952938d/1750526923/hls_264_master.m3u8?t=1536254441;steam_410710
