Set in a dark fantasy world, the game follows Geralt of Rivia, a monster hunter searching for his adopted daughter, Ciri, while navigating political conflicts and supernatural threats. Gameplay features exploration, combat, character progression, and branching narratives shaped by player choices. Widely acclaimed for its writing, world-building, and depth, it is considered one of the most influential RPGs of its generation.";Role-playing (RPG), Adventure;;gog_1207664643
2018 - Thronebreaker, The Witcher Tales (GOG);Thronebreaker: The Witcher Tales;Thronebreaker The Witcher Tales;\\madhdd02\Software\GAMES\GAMES COMPIL\THE WITCHER\2018 - Thronebreaker, The Witcher Tales (GOG);;OK;;2018;GOG;;;;"<b style=""display: block;text-align: center;""><h1>The Witcher World is Back! </h1></b>

